<!-- How to use the Data Table module: -->
<!-- This module is set up with special CSS classes in order to make it stack and not mess up our email layout on mobile devices. -->
<!-- Because of this, we have to hide the column headers on mobile, and inject the text back in to the layout with CSS -->
<!-- In order for this to work, we must change the "data-label" for the table cells so that they match the column headers. -->
<!-- ###################################################### -->
